dc_description_s: This ESRI Geodatabase contains polygon features and attribute data tables for census data for the country of Panama. The data is derived from the Instituto Nacional de Estadisticas y Censo and was released in 2013. The data contain 14,810 census boundary polygons that each have 81 attributes, and the lowest administrative boundary level represented is Barrios Urbanos. Refer to the documentation for a list of variables and a translation of variable titles into English. For more information on the census methodology and a glossary of variable categories, go to the INEC website at https://www.contraloria.gob.pa/inec/.
